  <description>

    <p> KatharaGUI is a simple GUI for the Kathara network emulation tool.                           </p>
    <p> It allows you to start and stop labs and connect to the containers in a convenient way.      </p>
    <p> KatharaGUI requires Docker to be installed and correctly configured on your system.          </p>

    <p> This app is written in Python and uses GTK 4, libadwaita, and VTE.                           </p>
  </description>

